          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to generate a summary of billing information at the account level for a specific billing period. It retrieves and aggregates data related to gas billing adjustments, including revised and canceled billed amounts, CCF (hundred cubic feet), and therms. The procedure uses data from several tables within the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Billing",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " schema, specifically focusing on the current processing period and a specific invoice account billing group."
